  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/ad091314b97d07939e711a139078129f.poster.avif?t=1773204215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/ad091314b97d07939e711a139078129f.webm?t=1773204215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/ad091314b97d07939e711a139078129f.mp4?t=1773204215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Repetendium</u> is a top-down roguelike-lite shooter. Select from a rowdy group of characters to play as and wield an ever expanding variety of gear and items to conquer the underworld. Death awaits...</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/4618bfb76d59011cf6603f4fbfe9484e.poster.avif?t=1773204215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/4618bfb76d59011cf6603f4fbfe9484e.webm?t=1773204215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/4618bfb76d59011cf6603f4fbfe9484e.mp4?t=1773204215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Early Access Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It has a chicken with a gun</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose from a large selection of weapons and abilities to match your play style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Level up and pick from unique items to expand your power</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fight against a variety of unique enemies and bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Compete for your place on the global leaderboard!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose between roguelike(no grind) or roguelite(grind grind grind)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Support for mouse & keyboard or controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other things that are <strong><i>cool</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/432d7a2083b6596b19ca4a7037d8f941.poster.avif?t=1773204215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/432d7a2083b6596b19ca4a7037d8f941.webm?t=1773204215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055500/extras/432d7a2083b6596b19ca4a7037d8f941.mp4?t=1773204215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
